{"lemma":"جَمّالُو","slug":"جَمّالُو","root":"ج.م.ل","root_slug":"ج-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَمّال","root":"جمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["name","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6351","n6352","n6361","n6362"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%91%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8F%D9%88"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَمُلَ (jamula) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"beauty","examples":[{"text":"وَلَكُمْ فِيهَا جَمَالٌ حِينَ تُرِيحُونَ وَحِينَ تَسْرَحُونَ","english":"There is in them [cattle] a beauty for you when you bring them home for rest and when you drive them forth to pasture."}]},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Jamal or Gamal"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of جَمَل (jamal)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"camel driver"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of جَمُلَ (jamula, “to be beautiful”).\n\nInflected form.\n\nOccupational noun derived from جَمَل (jamal, “camel”)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.maːl/","/d͡ʒi.maːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6351","headword_ar":"جَمَالٌ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamula","text_ar":"جَمُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, Msb:) [when used as a simple subst., meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Beauty, goodliness, comeliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasingness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusonN","text_ar":"حُسْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Mgh, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodness in action,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"actions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaviour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) or also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in moral character:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prettiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delicacy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"minuteness, of beauty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much goodness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beauty"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comeliness, in the mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the actions"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaviour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much goodness that is communicated from its possessor to another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) accord. to As, [when relating to the person,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusonN","text_ar":"حُسْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the eyes; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlN","text_ar":"جَمَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the nose. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hsn","text_ar":"حسن"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAlaka A^ano","text_ar":"جَمَالَكَ اَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tafoEala ka*aA","text_ar":"لَا تَفْعَلَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISd, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano tafoEala ka*aA","text_ar":"اَنْ تَفْعَلَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, TA,) meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keep to that which is most comely for thee to do, and do not thus."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, ISd, K. [But see what follows.]) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Patience."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xS","text_ar":"خص"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Aboo-Dhu-eyb says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"jamaAlaka A^ay~uhaA Alqalobu AlqariyHu\n                      \n                     \n                        sataloqaY mano tuHib~u fatasotariyHu"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA, the former of which cites only the first hemistich, and the latter substitutes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljariyHu","text_ar":"الجَرِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqariyHu","text_ar":"القَرِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) meaning, [Keep"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy patience, O thou wounded heart: thou wilt find whom thou lovest, and be at rest:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keep to thy patience,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy constraint of thyself to be patient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy shrinking from what is foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be not impatient in an evil manner."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","M","K","TA","Sb","ISd","IDrd"]},{"entry_id":"n6352","headword_ar":"جُمَالٌ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":       -A2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumaAlapN","text_ar":"جُمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6361","headword_ar":"جَمَّالٌ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An owner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an attendant, of a camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL, TA: * [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jAmilN","text_ar":"جامِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~aAlapN","text_ar":"جَمَّالَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"owners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attendants, of camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xay~aAlapN","text_ar":"خَيَّالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~aArapN","text_ar":"حَمَّارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) as the former is to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ham~aArN","text_ar":"حَمَّارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See an ex. of the latter in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA","text_ar":"اـِذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6362","headword_ar":"جُمَّالٌ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamiylN","text_ar":"جَمِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}